title: Doctor Who Complete Season 01, 1963-1964, William Hartnell [Upda
description:
[Update: removed duplicate mkv file]

All 42 episodes of the 1963/64 season of Doctor Who, featuring the First Doctor and his companions: Susan Foreman, Barbara Wright, and Ian Chesterton.

Includes reconstructions using photographs taken on set and recovered segments of footage, along with the audio recordings of the episodes, to recreate missing episodes. Visual quality varies depending on the reconstruction.
